N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 143.4 - Pre-notification requirement for shipments of regulated articles into the State of New York

State Regulations

Persons shipping regulated articles into the State of New

York shall pre-notify the Department, Division or Plant Industry, in writing, on a form prescribed by the Commissioner. Notes
